---
title: Parmesan Pan-Fried Gnocchi and Chicken with Spinach and Peas
description: Golden pan-fried gnocchi and hearty chicken add a delicious twist to a classic Alfredo! Rich cream and savoury Parmesan make a luscious sauce for this pasta supper.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/gnocchis-poeles-au-parmesan-et-poulet-64bfc669.jpg
